Executive Profile
Steven R. Shawley  Independent Director, Hubbell IncorporatedAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships64$220,261
Background

		Mr. Steven R. Shawley, also known as Steve, served as Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of Ingersoll-Rand Plc (also known as, Ingersoll-Rand Co. Ltd.) from June 2008 to September 27, 2013 and from August 01, 2005 to September 27, 2013 respectively. Mr. Shawley served as Executive Officer at Ingersoll-Rand Plc since September 2013. He served as the President of Climate Control Technologies Sector from August 1, 2005 to 2008 and President of Thermo King ... North America since August 2002 until 2003 at Ingersoll-Rand Plc. He served as a Vice President of Ingersoll-Rand Plc since June 1999 and as the President of Climate Control Americas from 2003 to 2005. He served as Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of Ingersoll Rand Corporation. He served as a Corporate Controller of Ingersoll-Rand from June 1998 to 2002. He joined Ingersoll-Rand in 1997 through the acquisition of Thermo King, a business of Westinghouse Electric Corporation, where he served as Vice President and Controller. At Thermo King, he was responsible for all finance, information technology and treasury activities. Prior to Thermo King, he held numerous other key financial positions with Westinghouse in a career that spaced over 20 years. Mr. Shawley has been an Independent Director of Hubbell Inc. since February 13, 2014. He served as a Director of GrafTech International Ltd. since May 2010. He is a Certified Management Accountant. Mr. Shawley holds a Bachelor of Science Degree from the University of Virginia and Masters Degree in Business Administration from the University of Pittsburgh.Read Full Background




